        "description": {
            "value": "<p>The blade of this <em>+2 greater striking @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Frost (Greater)] greatsword</em> appears to be nothing but icy shards. The <em>frost brand</em> automatically extinguishes non-magical fires in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:20]. While wielding it, you gain fire resistance 5.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> command, Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You swing the <em>frost brand</em> into the area of an ongoing magical fire, and the blade attempts to counteract the fire with a counteract modifier of [[/r 1d20+27 #Counteract]]{+27}. If it fails, it can't attempt to counteract the same fire again.</p>"
